Everything runs through Fourthwall — memberships, merch, and the storefront. One platform, one brand experience, one URL. Fourthwall is fully white-label, has native Twitch gifting integration, zero platform fee on physical products, and saves roughly $3,500 per year versus Patreon at 500 members. Discord handles community; Signal handles the inner circle.

